{"type":"message","id":"00c43ec0","parentId":"ab797dd7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:54:00.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总在问昨天（周一）的日报点评是否存到知识库了。让我检查一下知识库中是否有昨天的日报点评确认版文档。\n\n根据AGENTS.md中的规则：\n- 周一是点评上周五的日报\n- 归档需要执行3步：\n  1. 确认版文档 → 创建到知识库「日报点评确认版」文件夹\n  2. 多维表格 → 录入27个字段到「日报点评完整记录」\n  3. 汇总索引 → 更新「日报点评汇总」文档\n\n我需要检查知识库，看看昨天（周一，03-23）是否有完成归档。让我先搜索一下知识库中的日报点评确认版文档。","thinkingSignature":"c06e31b6031ab8e34643de5b4c996a486c8215037612c76b7618b26f66a9ebb4"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下知识库中昨天的日报点评归档情况。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pb8vgfd9q70c_1","name":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"日报点评确认版 03-23"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pb8vgfd9q70c_2","name":"feishu_wiki_space","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":228,"cacheRead":21187,"cacheWrite":28510,"totalTokens":50062,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0002736,"cacheRead":0.00063561,"cacheWrite":0.0034211999999999997,"total":0.0043715099999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774313634348}}
