{"type":"message","id":"ea89e144","parentId":"637fe3c8","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:56:01.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总在问我之前写的文档和运行系统，就是DJOS这些知识库内容。让我先看看TOOLS.md里提到的知识库核心文件清单：\n\n| 文件 | 知识库标题 | 位置 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| SOUL.md | SOUL灵魂文件 | 根目录 |\n| USER.md | USER用户信息 | 根目录 |\n| AGENTS.md | AGENTS工作手册 | 根目录 |\n| HEARTBEAT.md | HEARTBEAT心跳任务 | 根目录 |\n| TOOLS.md | TOOLS工具配置 | 根目录 |\n| 日报点评Skill | 日报点评Skill | 日报点评文件夹 |\n\n\n| 日报点评确认版 | 日报点评确认版 | 日报点评文件夹 |\n\n除了这些，我还建立了道简网络运行系统（DJRS），包含DJOS操作系统、DJMS管控系统和DJAS应用系统三个层次，共15个子系统。TOOLS.md第7节明确要求本地md文件是执行依据，而知识库是备份存档，每次修改md文件后必须同步更新知识库文档。\n\n检查一下DJRS相关的核心文档是否已同步到知识库——DJOS培训学习笔记、深度研究报告和行政子系统似乎都还没有对应的知识库同步记录。\n\n看起来DJOS/DJMS/DJAS的文档内容虽然存放在知识库中，但我还没有逐一验证TOOLS.md中列出的那些核心文档是否都已同步。我需要向姚总确认这一点，同时检查知识库中DJRS的完整状态。\n\n我已经完成了日报点评Skill和确认版的同步，但DJOS/DJMS/DJAS这些关键文档还需要逐一对应TOOLS.md中的清单来确认是否都已上传。","thinkingSignature":"9a7ad2d47b3ccc4f5881328365fe173afe55a7e74929d8941b4d3be8e84f74fa"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！您问的是DJRS（道简网络运行系统）的文档是否存到知识库了。\n\n让我检查一下这些核心文档的同步情况：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0gyg21au62cm_1","name":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"道简网络运行系统"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0gyg21au62cm_2","name":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"DJOS"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":456,"cacheRead":49577,"cacheWrite":19994,"totalTokens":70164,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0005472,"cacheRead":0.00148731,"cacheWrite":0.0023992799999999997,"total":0.00447489}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774313749157}}
{"type":"message","id":"0aec839d","parentId":"ea89e144","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:56:02.412Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0gyg21au62cm_1","toolName":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"total\": 32,\n  \"has_more\": true,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:02+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"SyXWd8bUKoKVuKxxbp6cpdCKn6c\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:04+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/SyXWd8bUKoKVuKxxbp6cpdCKn6c\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"行政管理子<h>系统</h>（DJAS-XZ）是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）应用层（DJAS）的支撑性子<h>系统</h>，专注于行政管理的工具化和<h>系统</h>化，与DJOS-XZ配套：DJOS-XZ定义&#34;如何做&#34;，DJAS-XZ定义&#34;用什么工具做&#34;。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"DJAS-XZ 行政管理子<h>系统</h>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:41:44+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"D6NNdWl1tosxsMxeQG6cR8DQn1c\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:41:47+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/D6NNdWl1tosxsMxeQG6cR8DQn1c\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"财务管理子<h>系统</h>（DJAS-CW）是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）应用层（DJAS）的核心子<h>系统</h>之一，专注于公司财务全流程管理，关注&#34;用什么工具和<h>系统</h>进行财务管理&#34;。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"DJAS-CW 财务管理子<h>系统</h>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:16+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"ZpT6d2kuxovg83xonSwc8KjAnDV\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:20+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/ZpT6d2kuxovg83xonSwc8KjAnDV\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"项目管理子<h>系统</h>（DJAS-XM）是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）应用层（DJAS）的核心子<h>系统</h>之一，专注于项目全生命周期管理，关注&#34;用什么工具和流程管理项目&#34;。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"DJAS-XM 项目管理子<h>系统</h>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:17+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"TvRadc8k8onGmZxNsQrc6MQjnPB\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:19+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/TvRadc8k8onGmZxNsQrc6MQjnPB\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"合同管理子<h>系统</h>（DJAS-HT）是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）应用层（DJAS）的核心子<h>系统</h>之一，专注于合同全流程管理，关注&#34;用什么工具和流程管理合同&#34;。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"DJAS-HT 合同管理子<h>系统</h>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:41+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"NghCd2NhForoskxrpHZceOM6n7f\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:42:44+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/NghCd2NhForoskxrpHZceOM6n7f\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"客户管理子<h>系统</h>（DJAS-KH）是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）应用层（DJAS）的核心子<h>系统</h>之一，专注于客户关系管理，关注&#34;用什么工具和方法管理客户关系&#34;。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"DJAS-KH 客户管理子<h>系统</h>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:28:46+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"JliWdP1rXoHjAexkQOzcg5S3n6c\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:28:49+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/JliWdP1rXoHjAexkQOzcg5S3n6c\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"风险管控子<h>系统</h>是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）管控层的风险屏障，承担着识别、评估、监控和应对企业内外部风险的关键职能，是 DJMS 五大子<h>系统</h>的安全保障中心。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"风险管控子<h>系统</h>（DJMS-FX）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:28:29+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"Gx6tdmUbYo5QfcxKBIEc9FDGnWf\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:28:30+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/Gx6tdmUbYo5QfcxKBIEc9FDGnWf\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"战略管控子<h>系统</h>是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）的管控核心层，承担着企业长期发展方向与重大决策管控的关键职能，是 DJMS 五大子<h>系统</h>之首，决定公司&#34;做什么、不做什么&#34;。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"战略管控子<h>系统</h>（DJMS-ZL）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:18:15+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"U56PdpsBrojAmtxCNNkcM6BWnme\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:18:16+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/U56PdpsBrojAmtxCNNkcM6BWnme\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"产品子<h>系统</h>是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）的核心组成部分，承担着研发、生产、供应、销售的关键职能，是企业核心竞争力的根基。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"产品子<h>系统</h>（5.1-DJOS-CP）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:16:03+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"LegidUf6GorJSaxchqQcOxEunKc\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:50:59+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/LegidUf6GorJSaxchqQcOxEunKc\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"服务子<h>系统</h>是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）的核心组成部分，承担着客户满意与口碑建设的关键职能，是企业To B科技服务的核心竞争力保障。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"服务子<h>系统</h>（3.1-DJOS-FW）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:17:13+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:17:14+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"营销子<h>系统</h>是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）的核心组成部分，承担着客源拓展、项目获取、收入增长的关键职能，是企业发展的核心引擎。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"营销子<h>系统</h>（4.1-DJOS-YX）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:28:29+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"BPyadoyzooeFqWx1QzBciNhknab\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:28:32+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/BPyadoyzooeFqWx1QzBciNhknab\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"计划预算子<h>系统</h>是<h>道简网络运行系统</h>（DJRS）管控层的资源配置枢纽，承担着将战略目标转化为可执行计划、将战略意图落地为财务预算的关键职能，是 DJMS 五大子<h>系统</h>的资源调配中心。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"计划预算管控子<h>系统</h>（DJMS-JS）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-03T10:44:34+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n    