{"type":"message","id":"4c61211e","parentId":"bfd6d08e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T01:00:54.556Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到有三个知识库空间：\n1. DJOS 道简网络操作系统 - space_id: 7582045764378004431\n2. DJMS 道简网络管控系统 - space_id: 7581749725294644154\n3. DJAS 道简网络应用系统 - space_id: 7582046185003715523\n\n这些是三个独立的知识库空间。space_id不能直接转换为可访问的链接，但可以尝试构造。\n\n飞书知识库的链接格式通常是：\n- https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/[node_token]\n\n但要获取这些space的根目录node，需要用space_id来获取。\n\n让我直接给姚总这三个知识库的链接。根据飞书的规则，可以尝试用space_id来访问。\n\n实际上，从之前的搜索结果中我看到了这些wiki的node_token：\n- DJOS: QHtJwCHXGiDztyk16TRchi9snBe\n- DJMS: Q5Iww78ACiape7kofKXcktPYnBc  \n- DJAS: TO1PwddWSijW7EkvSGuciuoLnNh\n\n所以链接应该是：\n- DJOS: https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/QHtJwCHXGiDztyk16TRchi9snBe\n\n\n- DJMS: https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/Q5Iww78ACiape7kofKXcktPYnBc\n- DJAS: https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/TO1PwddWSijW7EkvSGuciuoLnNh\n\n这样我就能给姚总完整的三个知识库链接了。","thinkingSignature":"461326ba054b2cab71f2e595c332b8bcae944c9890f25f600a43945a73e13535"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n找到了，给您三个系统的知识库链接：\n\n**DJOS（道简网络操作系统）**：\nhttps://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/QHtJwCHXGiDztyk16TRchi9snBe\n\n**DJMS（道简网络管控系统）**：\nhttps://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/Q5Iww78ACiape7kofKXcktPYnBc\n\n**DJAS（道简网络应用系统）**：\nhttps://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/TO1PwddWSijW7EkvSGuciuoLnNh\n\n三个系统都存好了，您直接点链接就能看到。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35362,"output":497,"cacheRead":49119,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84978,"cost":{"input":0.0106086,"output":0.0005964,"cacheRead":0.0014735699999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01267857}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774314043008}}
