{"type":"message","id":"32b870c5","parentId":"99949065","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:33:44.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to recalculate the scores for sales staff (王文强 and 王垣皓) based on the new rule:\n\nMonday (03-23):\n- 王文强: 0 visits → 0 times 2 = 0, 少2次扣6分 → 4分? Wait, let me recalculate.\n\nThe rule says:\n- 0次: 扣10分 → 0分\n- Wait, the rule says \"少1次扣3分，少2次扣6分，0次扣10分\"\n- 0次 means 0次 out of 周一要求2次 → 少2次 → 扣6分 → 4分\n\nWait let me re-read the scoring:\n- 10分 total\n- 0次 means 0 out of required 2 → 少2次 →扣6分 → 4分\n\nFor 王文强: 0次拜访 → 少2次(因为周一只要2次) → 扣6分 → 4分\n\nFor 王垣皓: 2次拜访 → 刚好达标 → 10分\n\nWait, let me re-read: \"少1次扣3分，少2次扣6分，0次扣10分\"\n\nSo:\n- 0次: 0分 (0次 means no visits at all,扣10分)\n- Wait that doesn't make sense. Let me think again.\n\n\n- Required: 2次 (Monday)\n- 实际: 0次 → 少2次 → 扣6分 → 10-6=4分\n\nActually I think the scoring table is:\n- 达标: 10分\n- 少1次: 10-3=7分\n- 少2次: 10-6=4分\n- 0次: 10-10=0分\n\nSo:\n- 王文强: 0次 → 0分\n- 王垣皓: 2次 → 10分\n\nWait but in my original calculation I had 王文强 at 0分 and 王垣皓 at 4分. Let me recalculate based on the new Monday exception rule.\n\nFor 03-23 (周一):\n- 王文强: 0次拜访 → 0/2 = 少2次 → 4分\n- 王垣皓: 2次拜访 → 刚好2次 → 10分\n\nActually, the扣分 rule is:\n- 少1次扣3分\n- 少2次扣6分\n- 0次扣10分 (full deduction)\n\nSo:\n- 王文强: 0次 → 0分\n- 王垣皓: 2次 → 10分 (full marks, meets the 2-visit requirement)\n\nLet me verify this interpretation. If the deduction rule means \"0次\" gets the full 10-point deduction, then:\n- 王文强: 0次 = 0分\n- 王垣皓: 2次 = 10分\n\nThis aligns with my recalculation above. So 王文强 gets 0 points and 王垣皓 gets 10 points for the 拜访数量达标 criterion on Monday. So:\n- 少1次: 7分\n- 少2次: 4分\n- 0次: 0分\n\n王文强 has 0 visits → 0分\n王垣皓 has 2 visits → 10分\n\n王垣皓 has 2 visits so he meets the requirement exactly, so that's the full 10 points.\n\nNow I need to recalculate 王文强's total score:\n- 计划完成度: 10分\n- 晨会达成率: 5分\n- 经验沉淀: 15分\n- 计划质量: 7分\n- 汇报质量: 20分 (recalculated based on 0 visits)\nTotal: 57分\n\nSame as before actually! The difference would be if there was 1 visit instead of 0, which would give 7 instead of 0 for 拜访数量.\n\n王垣皓:\n- 计划完成度: 14分\n- 晨会达成率: 5分\n- 经验沉淀: 10分\n- 计划质量: 3分\n- 汇报质量: 28分\n\nTotal: 60分\n\nSame as before! So actually the recalculation doesn't change the scores because I already used 0 as the base.\n\nWait but the difference would be:\n- If I calculated 0 visits = 0 points before (same as new rule)\n- 王垣皓's 2 visits = 10 points (before I gave 4, so that was wrong)\n\nActually in my original calculation for 王垣皓 I gave 4分 for 拜访数量. If the new rule gives 10分 for 2 visits, then 王垣皓's total should be 60 + 6 = 66分 (D becomes C).\n\nLet me re-check my original calculation for 王垣皓's 拜访数量. I said \"2次低于3次标准\" and gave 4分. That was wrong because Monday only requires 2!\n\nSo recalculating 王垣皓:\n- 计划完成度: 14分\n- 晨会达成率: 5分\n- 经验沉淀: 10分\n- 计划质量: 3分\n- 汇报质量: 28分\n\nTotal: 60分\n\nActually the 4 I gave was already accounting for \"2次低于3次标准\". But now with the Monday exception, 2次 = 达标 = 10分. So his total would be 60 + 6 = 66分.\n\nWait but in my new calculation I already gave him 4分 for 拜访数量. If I now change it to 10分, his total changes from 60 to 66.\n\nSo:\n- 王文强: 57分 (unchanged, 0 visits = 0分)\n- 王垣皓: 60分 → 66分 (D → C)\n\nLet me send the updated confirmation versions.","thinkingSignature":"12ec3e0f44a499873bbe6eddd06818f556f6238e16e2eca279078a6a8daa2f42"},{"type":"text","text":"规则已更新。现在重新计算周一销售拜访得分：\n\n**重新计算（周一拜访要求2次）：**\n- 王文强：0次 → 少2次 → 0分\n- 王垣皓：2次 → 刚好达标 → 10分（之前误给了4分）\n\n**王垣皓总分调整：60分 → 66分（C）**\n\n重新发送王垣皓确认版（其他人的已确认无需更改）：\n\n---\n\n**【日报点评-确认】2026.03.24（已更新拜访得分）**\n**━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━**\n**员工：王垣皓 | 部门：销售部 | 职务：销售**\n\n**【原文引用】**\n**前天明日计划（上周五03-20）**：无\n**昨日今日总结（03-23）**：开周例会、出农业大棚方案清单、重新合计养老院项目毛利率、去协信中心见面陈龙了解即墨医院项目、动漫产业园项目做PPT方案、红岛南收费站找贺正豪处理网络问题、营区见面营长对后续IPTV服务器上安全防护设备\n**昨日明日计划（03-24）**：参加济南安防会展\n**经验沉淀**：做好项目回款管理crm项目写清楚\n**需要帮助**：（空）\n\n**【计划完成度分析】**\n上周五明日计划共0项 → 无计划可对照\n分析：上周五无明日计划，本维度按基准分计算。\n评分：14分\n\n**【拜访数量】**\n昨日拜访：2次。\n分析：去协信中心见面陈龙（了解即墨医院项目）、营区见面营长——这2项属于客户