{"type":"message","id":"2bb49acc","parentId":"6275d8b0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:15:15.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是有问题。让我看一下之前成功的记录返回格式...之前成功的batch_create返回了records，其中\"文本\"字段的值是员工姓名。可能是\"文本\"字段作为主键是自动生成的，不能手动传。\n\n但问题是为什么现在报错FieldNameNotFound。让我检查一下是不是因为某些字段名有问题。\n\n看一下字段列表：\n- 文本 (field_name)\n- 发送状态\n- 点评日期\n- 员工姓名\n- 部门\n- 职务\n- 总分\n- 等级\n- ...\n\n我传的字段名应该是对的。可能问题是batch_create和create的参数格式不一样？\n\nbatch_create用records数组，每个record是{fields: {...}}\ncreate直接用fields: {...}\n\n让我再仔细看看batch_create的描述...records参数是array of records，每个record需要fields属性。\n\n等等，我发现问题了！我在batch_create里传的是records数组，但每条记录的fields里面包含了所有字段。但问题可能是某些字段的值格式不对。\n\n让我分条逐个字段检查...\n\n实际上让我先尝试用batch_create只创建一条最简单的记录看看能否成功。","thinkingSignature":"3c2bdca7aad80c6279f560ee759ed3a23fd687f9b221d1e65bcadc76ae94e9fd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ilc1glk3q2y_1","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"batch_create","app_token":"V21jbyhuladTb3specIctqgtnKb","table_id":"tblwrvm2TgJpfaS4","records":[{"fields":{"文本":"王文强-2026-03-24","发送状态":"已发送","员工姓名":"王文强"}}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114949,"output":341,"cacheRead":49568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164858,"cost":{"input":0.0344847,"output":0.00040919999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0014870399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03638094}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774322102719}}
