{"type":"compaction","id":"3b1644f3","parentId":"52faef1e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:42:04.247Z","summary":"## Decisions\n\n- **Monday plan rule**: When reviewing Monday reports, \"前天明日计划\" = 上周五明日计划. If Friday's plan was \"休息/暂无/无\", counts as no plan → plan completion rate = 0\n- **Monday sales visit rule**: Sales staff only need 2 visits on Mondays (reduced from 3) due to half-day meeting\n- **Confirmation versions**: Must send one per employee as separate messages\n- **300-character minimum**: Each confirmation version must be ≥300 characters with detailed analysis in each section\n- **Friday plans from 03-20 used for 03-23 review**:\n  - 王文强: 2 items (荣柏大厦对接, 周例会) → completed 1 = 50% → 10pts\n  - 王垣皓: \"无\" → 0pts\n  - 刘世龙: \"暂无\" → 0pts\n  - 胡文正: \"休息\" → 0pts (not 100% completion, counts as no plan)\n  - 郝彦艳: \"无\" → 0pts\n  - 李文娅: \"暂无\" → 0pts\n  - 刘晓: 6 items, completed 5 = 83% → 25pts\n\n## Open TODOs\n\n- [ ] Await 姚总 confirmation on 王垣皓 full version (46pts E, just re-sent)\n- [ ] Send 刘世龙 confirmation version (54pts D)\n- [ ] Send 胡文正 confirmation version (35pts E)\n- [ ] Send 郝彦艳 confirmation version (45pts E)\n- [ ] Send 李文娅 confirmation version (57pts D)\n- [ ] After all 7 confirmed → send employee versions to each staff member\n- [ ] Archive to knowledge base (确认版 doc + 多维表格录入 + 汇总索引更新)\n- [ ] Sync MEMORY.md updates to 知识库 日报点评Skill document\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n\n- 确认版分开发送，每位员工单独一条消息\n- 确认版点评每份不得少于300字\n- 原文引用必须包含**前天明日计划（上周五）**\n- 飞书汇报应用 chat_id: `oc_acfe8996065b7ac35d7463d96e37f14b`\n- 销售群 chat_id: `oc_8804331487d36fc9bf177a83e780f726`\n- 晨会纪要 doc_id: `Vd4NdcwAzopWxNxbUo5chq19nRe`\n- 多维表格 app_token: `V21jbyhuladTb3specIctqgtnKb`, table_id: `tblwrvm2TgJpfaS4`\n- Skill file: `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/daily-report-review/SKILL.md`\n\n## Pending User Asks\n\n- 姚总 has not explicitly confirmed any employee review yet (aside from being dissatisfied with brief version of 王垣皓 and re-sending)\n\n## Exact Identifiers\n\n- **Knowledge 