\n## Critical Context\n- User is 姚霖 (ID: ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\n- This appears to be a continuation of an ongoing task about managing daily report reviews\n- Previous context about whose reports and specific report content is not provided in this segment\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n- **Batch confirmation workflow**: When user says \"发日报点评确认版\", send all daily report reviews for everyone together for one-time confirmation\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Wait for user's signal to send daily report review confirmation version\n- Prepare all team members' daily report reviews for batch delivery\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Send all reports together when user requests confirmation version\n- No individual submissions - must be batched\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User will say \"发日报点评确认版\" to trigger sending all daily report reviews at once\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Message ID: `om_x100b532b83ca88acc228405c538e0aa`\n- Sender ID: `ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b`\n- Sender name: `姚霖`\n- Timestamp: `Tue 2026-03-24 10:54 GMT+8`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-03-24 10:43:23 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b532bea648880c14ca30db9f218f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b532bea648880c14ca30db9f218f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 10:43 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n不是确认版不少于300字，而是点评不少于300字，确认版不能少于1000字，写到记忆及技能里。而且在任何情况下都不允许犯错\n- Assistant: 姚总批评得对！我理解错了规则，立即更正并更新到记忆和技能：\n\n**规则更新：**\n- **确认版整体不少于1000字**\n- **点评部分不少于300字**\n- **任何情况下都不允许犯错**\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (edit): Successfully replaced text in /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/MEMORY.md.\n- Assistant: [non