{"type":"message","id":"f9976afd","parentId":"91a0a666","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:45:40.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to store the important learnings and decisions from today's session into memory/2026-03-24.md. Let me check if this file already exists first.\n\nKey learnings to store:\n1. 确认版整体不少于1000字，点评部分不少于300字\n2. 确认版 = 员工版，发给员工的内容就是确认版内容\n3. 员工版格式：做得好的 + 需改进 + 建议 + 总分（一字不差）\n4. 以后发日报点评确认版时，把所有人的确认版一次性全部发完（每人单独一条消息），姚总一次性确认即可\n\n\n5. 多维表格的batch_create对字段数量有限制，需要分批创建记录\n6. 飞书消息content中的JSON字符串需要严格格式化，\\n会导致解析错误\n\nNow I'll check if memory/2026-03-24.md exists.","thinkingSignature":"da316dfb7e612e9e96d60541c989935211eb0b44faf20a4e4941220334d2adcd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b1erlduukruy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-03-24.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":226,"cacheRead":21187,"cacheWrite":74519,"totalTokens":96069,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0.00063561,"cacheWrite":0.008942279999999999,"total":0.009890189999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774323930403}}
