{"type":"message","id":"909d68a4","parentId":"236052c8","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:52:45.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 7 employees have been sent the correct employee versions. The content is now exactly matching the confirmation version's 做得好的, 需改进, 建议 sections plus the total score. I've also updated the rules in SOUL.md and SKILL.md.\n\nLet me report completion.","thinkingSignature":"ec3f46a3dd873a7cf47659d239780e0f95db19e6533f8d048524ff0eff7ff877"},{"type":"text","text":"**7人全部发送完毕！**\n\n本次发送内容与确认版一字不差：\n- 做得好的（确认版原文）\n- 需改进（确认版原文）\n- 建议（确认版原文）\n- 总分：XX分\n\n规则已更新到SOUL.md和SKILL.md最高优先级位置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56445,"output":127,"cacheRead":49568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106140,"cost":{"input":0.0169335,"output":0.0001524,"cacheRead":0.0014870399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01857294}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774324361164}}
