{"type":"message","id":"d4b168db","parentId":"56718563","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:39:22.202Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8qr521y3ftb1_1","toolName":"feishu_fetch_doc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"doc_id\":\"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\",\"has_more\":true,\"length\":428,\"log_id\":\"20260324133921AC9B59B9FE3C19D25210\",\"markdown\":\"行系统（DJRS）营销子系统（DJOS-YX）的标准操作规范，旨在为公司营销管理团队提供统一、可执行、可量化的作业标准。通过规范化客户开发、客户关系、销售管理、报价管理、合同管理、渠道管理、市场推广、销售团队管理八大核心模块，确保公司营销工作高效有序，支撑道简网络整体经营目标的实现。道简网络主营企业\",\"message\":\"Document fetched successfully\",\"next_offset\":230,\"offset\":80,\"title\":\"营销子系统（4.1-DJOS-YX）\",\"total_length\":24965}"}],"details":{"doc_id":"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb","has_more":true,"length":428,"log_id":"20260324133921AC9B59B9FE3C19D25210","markdown":"行系统（DJRS）营销子系统（DJOS-YX）的标准操作规范，旨在为公司营销管理团队提供统一、可执行、可量化的作业标准。通过规范化客户开发、客户关系、销售管理、报价管理、合同管理、渠道管理、市场推广、销售团队管理八大核心模块，确保公司营销工作高效有序，支撑道简网络整体经营目标的实现。道简网络主营企业","message":"Document fetched successfully","next_offset":230,"offset":80,"title":"营销子系统（4.1-DJOS-YX）","total_length":24965},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774330762153}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8cb0230","parentId":"d4b168db","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:39:33.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! The营销子系统 (DJOS-YX) document mentions these modules:\n- 客户开发\n- 客户关系\n- 销售管理\n- 报价管理\n- 合同管理\n- 渠道管理\n- 市场推广\n- 销售团队管理\n\nThese are different from what I thought were the standard sub-modules! The standard sub-modules should be:\n1. 行政子系统\n2. 培训子系统\n3. 服务子系统\n4. 营销子系统\n5. 产品子系统\n\nBut inside each subsystem, there are specific modules. For example, the营销子系统 should contain营销-specific modules like客户开发, 报价管理, 合同管理, etc.\n\nWait, but姚总 said \"子模块完全按照这个图上的来\". Looking at the image姚总 showed earlier, the chart showed the 5 main subsystems at the top level, not the detailed modules within each.\n\nActually, looking at the chart more carefully from the image:\n- The left side shows: 营销子系统, 服务子系统, 产品子系统 (these are the 5 subsystems)\n- Each subsystem has its own detailed modules\n\nSo when姚总 says \"子模块完全按照这个图上的来\", I think the issue is that within the营销子系统 (or any subsystem), the detailed modules/流程 need to match what's in the standard format chart.\n\nLet me continue fetching the营销子系统 to see its actual structure and compare it with the expected structure from the chart.","thinkingSignature":"a00901484ed390b6dc62e30af9fe59d21d6b870ef1c0c3f5d9f66b47eb41c533"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f4hnpedu2gu7_1","name":"feishu_fetch_doc","arguments":{"doc_id":"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb","offset":230,"limit":200}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68033,"output":364,"cacheRead":49568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117965,"cost":{"input":0.020409899999999998,"output":0.0004368,"cacheRead":0.0014870399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022333739999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774330762200}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3ae5da9","parentId":"d8cb0230","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:39:35.451Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f4hnpedu2gu7_1","toolName":"feishu_fetch_doc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"doc_id\":\"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\",\"has_more\":true,\"length\":542,\"log_id\":\"20260324133934673AA7E023DE3DCAF9A5\",\"markdown\":\"数字化解决方案、智能安防与弱电工程、系统集成、IT全周期运维服务，营销是公司收入增长的发动机，覆盖从市场拓展到合同签约的全流程，是公司持续发展的核心驱动力。\\n### 2. 适用范围\\n本手册适用于道简网络全体涉及营销管理的员工，覆盖以下管理场景：\\n- 目标客户定位与客户开发\\n- 客户关系建立与维护管理\\n- 销售机会跟进与项目成交\\n- 产品报价与价格策略管理\\n- 合同条款谈判与合同签订\\n- 渠道合作伙\",\"message\":\"Document fetched successfully\",\"next_offset\":430,\"offset\":230,\"title\":\"营销子系统（4.1-DJOS-YX）\",\"total_length\":24965}"}],"details":{"doc_id":"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb","has_more":true,"length":542,"log_id":"20260324133934673AA7E023DE3DCAF9A5","markdown":"数字化解决方案、智能安防与弱电工程、系统集成、IT全周期运维服务，营销是公司收入增长的发动机，覆盖从市场拓展到合同签约的全流程，是公司持续发展的核心驱动力。\n### 2. 适用范围\n本手册适用于道简网络全体涉及营销管理的员工，覆盖以下管理场景：\n- 目标客户定位与客户开发\n- 客户关系建立与维护管理\n- 销售机会跟进与项目成交\n- 产品报价与价格策略管理\n- 合同条款谈判与合同签订\n- 渠道合作伙","message":"Document fetched successfully","next_offset":430,"offset":230,"title":"营销子系统（4.1-DJOS-YX）","total_length":24965},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774330775402}}
