{"type":"message","id":"a756a7dd","parentId":"540af1d6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:05:01.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"三个行政子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）都已优化完成。现在向姚总汇报进度。","thinkingSignature":"dc39d88cf605d3e2893241ed99d2a5bd8b44d4745e448ebe878d4b8ca99b66f8"},{"type":"text","text":"**行政子系统三个层次全部优化完成！**\n\n| 系统 | 文档 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **DJOS**（如何做） | [行政子系统（1.1-DJOS-XZ）](https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/Iy8zwYL2fi5N5bkIRvucEOTXnoc) | ✅ 已优化 |\n| **DJMS**（管什么） | [行政子系统（1.2-DJMS-XZ）](https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/PpkCwYT4CiMnUbksalxc82Htnjc) | ✅ 已优化 |\n| **DJAS**（用什么工具） | [行政子系统（1.3-DJAS-XZ）](https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/L0Yfw2SfTiGjobkK5uBcs7I1n3g) | ✅ 已优化 |\n\n三个文档均按标准格式优化：\n1. 前言（文档目的、适用范围、核心原则表格）\n2. 概述（定位与职责、模块架构表格）\n3. 一级流程（全景图、模块关联图）\n4. 各模块详细流程（模块职责、一级流程、详细流程与表格）\n5. 执行保障（监控指标表、持续优化机制）\n6. 相关附件清单（申请表/报告清单）\n7. 文档审批记录\n\n请姚总确认是否还需要优化其他子系统？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88275,"output":336,"cacheRead":49568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138179,"cost":{"input":0.0264825,"output":0.0004032,"cacheRead":0.0014870399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028372739999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774332286744}}
{"type":"message","id":"327d2167","parentId":"a756a7dd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:06:53.573Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 14:06:52 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b5316d17dc0b8b373da0722e37c2]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5316d17dc0b8b373da0722e37c2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 14:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n持续不断的优化，优化后的文档发我链接"}],"timestamp":1774332413564}}
{"type":"message","id":"daa0d328","parentId":"327d2167","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:07:11.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总让我继续优化其他子系统，并发送优化后的文档链接。我需要继续优化剩下的子系统。按照之前讨论的框架，5个子模块：行政、培训、服务、营销、产品，每个在DJOS/DJMS/DJAS三层都要优化。\n\n已经完成：行政子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n\n还需要优化：\n- 培训子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n- 服务子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n- 营销子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n- 产品子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n\n我需要先找到这些子系统的现有文档，然后逐一优化。让我先搜索一下。","thinkingSignature":"efb66e8890bc2303b1d647852bfeaf43d2b5602dd47837a54278e04ee0c8f0ed"},{"type":"text","text":"继续优化其他子系统。先查看现有子系统状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zvz0d6k7pf0r_1","name":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"培训子系统 DJOS"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":193,"cacheRead":49568,"cacheWrite":87729,"totalTokens":137627,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0002316,"cacheRead":0.0014870399999999998,"cacheWrite":0.010527479999999999,"total":0.012287219999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774332413567}}
