{"type":"message","id":"1fa80827","parentId":"9232c12e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:14:21.478Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_825v1orengeq_1","toolName":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"has_more\": false,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2025-12-24T15:56:27+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-09T11:45:54+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"IXhwwpeS7iWblpkVHchcqrT4nJg\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:27:32+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/IXhwwpeS7iWblpkVHchcqrT4nJg\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"<h>服务</h>应用<h>系统</h>（<h>DJAS</h>-FW）是公司IT运维<h>服务</h>工作的数字化支撑平台，为运维<h>服务</h>团队提供工单管理、监控告警、远程运维、客户门户全流程数字化<h>服务</h>。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>服务子系统</h>（3.3-<h>DJAS</h>-FW）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:16:03+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"LegidUf6GorJSaxchqQcOxEunKc\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:50:59+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/LegidUf6GorJSaxchqQcOxEunKc\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"本手册是道简网络<h>服务子系统</h>（<h>DJAS</h>-FW）的标准操作规范，旨在为公司<h>服务</h>管理团队提供统一、可执行、可量化的作业标准。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>服务子系统</h>（3.1-<h>DJ</h>OS-FW）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-09T11:20:42+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"E1sXwmUw1iAEY1kbrLwcXUj7npe\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T12:36:16+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/E1sXwmUw1iAEY1kbrLwcXUj7npe\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"本<h>子系统</h>与营销<h>子系统</h>（<h>DJ</h>OS-YX）、<h>服务子系统</h>（<h>DJ</h>OS-FW）深度协同，共同构成道简网络以产品为核心的业务支撑体系。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"产品<h>子系统</h>（5.1-<h>DJ</h>OS-CP）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T00:15:42+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:58:22+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"Ld7cws0IZipqubkyXc0cffZEn8d\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T00:15:43+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/Ld7cws0IZipqubkyXc0cffZEn8d\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"应用<h>系统</h>（<h>DJAS</h>）   <h>服务子系统</h>\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"道简网络操作<h>系统</h>培训学习笔记\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-01-27T15:11:41+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"BITABLE\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_0f8941658f62e4ad0313009680491588\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"李文娅\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-11T15:14:41+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \