{"type":"message","id":"d3c4a4c0","parentId":"a77d08ac","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:15:37.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"服务子系统三个层次全部优化完成！现在继续优化营销子系统和产品子系统。让我先汇报目前完成情况，然后继续优化。\n\n已完成：\n1. 行政子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n2. 培训子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n3. 服务子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n\n还需要：\n4. 营销子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n5. 产品子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n\n让我继续优化。","thinkingSignature":"f05b0744598e5fda299dfbff198a6324be5581fab5bc2ea57c5fff1cab51a94c"},{"type":"text","text":"**服务子系统三个层次全部优化完成！**\n\n目前已完成：\n- ✅ 行政子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n- ✅ 培训子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n- ✅ 服务子系统（DJOS/DJMS/DJAS）\n\n继续优化**营销子系统**：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g3qebb84eudh_1","name":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"营销子系统 DJOS"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116091,"output":216,"cacheRead":49568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":165875,"cost":{"input":0.0348273,"output":0.0002592,"cacheRead":0.0014870399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03657354}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774332928315}}
{"type":"message","id":"a27bd687","parentId":"d3c4a4c0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:15:38.952Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_g3qebb84eudh_1","toolName":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"total\": 12,\n  \"has_more\": false,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-24T03:17:13+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-24T08:57:01+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"本手册是道简网络运行系统（<h>DJ</h>RS）<h>营销子系统</h>（<h>DJOS</h>-YX）的标准操作规范，旨在为公司<h>营销</h>管理团队提供统一、可执行、可量化的作业标准。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>营销子系统</h>（4.1-<h>DJOS</h>-YX）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-09T11:20:42+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-24T00:34:10+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"姚霖\",\n        \"token\": \"POlgwSfUGiVzLsk1ZDeckpFKnRE\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-09T11:20:42+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/POlgwSfUGiVzLsk1ZDeckpFKnRE\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"4.1-<h>DJOS</h>-YX 道简网络操作系统-<h>营销子系统</h>_02.png\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>营销子系统</h>（4.1-<h>DJOS</h>-YX）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n    