hted\": \"销售管理是<h>营销子系统</h>（<h>DJOS</h>-YX）的核心模块之一，负责公司销售业务的全流程管理，从商机跟进到合同签订，确保销售目标的达成。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"4.1.6 销售管理\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"page_token\": \"{\\\"Mode\\\":0,\\\"GeoStrategyInfos\\\":{\\\"eu_nc\\\":{\\\"Mode\\\":0,\\\"Size\\\":20,\\\"Offset\\\":12,\\\"PreviousOffset\\\":0,\\\"Total\\\":12,\\\"strategies_infos\\\":[{\\\"strategies\\\":{},\\\"before_current_strategy_have_recalled_count\\\":0},{\\\"strategies\\\":{},\\\"before_current_strategy_have_recalled_count\\\":12}],\\\"last_strategy_infos\\\":{\\\"strategies\\\":{},\\\"before_current_strategy_have_recalled_count\\\":0},\\\"search_cold\\\":true}},\\\"size\\\":20,\\\"offset\\\":12,\\\"total\\\":12,\\\"shown_recordids_cache_Key\\\":\\\"7133889645745618945_9633499c-c35b-430c-9b8d-28d77517deb9_1774332938874127651\\\",\\\"search_cold\\\":true}\"\n}"}],"details":{"total":12,"has_more":false,"results":[{"entity_type":"DOC","result_meta":{"create_time":"2026-03-24T03:17:13+08:00","doc_types":"DOCX","edit_user_id":"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","edit_user_name":"姚霖","is_cross_tenant":false,"last_open_time":"1970-01-01T08:00:00+08:00","owner_id":"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","owner_name":"姚霖","token":"GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb","update_time":"2026-03-24T08:57:01+08:00","url":"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/docx/GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb"},"summary_highlighted":"本手册是道简网络运行系统（<h>DJ</h>RS）<h>营销子系统</h>（<h>DJOS</h>-YX）的标准操作规范，旨在为公司<h>营销</h>管理团队提供统一、可执行、可量化的作业标准。","title_highlighted":"<h>营销子系统</h>（4.1-<h>DJOS</h>-YX）"},{"entity_type":"WIKI","result_meta":{"create_time":"2026-03-09T11:20:42+08:00","doc_types":"DOCX","edit_user_id":"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","edit_user_name":"姚霖","last_open_time":"2026-03-24T00:34:10+08:00","owner_id":"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b","owner_name":"姚霖","token":"POlgwSfUGiVzLsk1ZDeckpFKnRE","update_time":"2026-03-09T11:20:42+08:00","url":"https://qddaojian.feishu.cn/wiki/POlgwSfUGiVzLsk1ZDeckpFKnRE"},"summary_highlighted":"4.1-<h>DJOS</h>-Y