{"type":"message","id":"b813d6d6","parentId":"7f20eaa6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:05:44.282Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/ca592e6f-a30c-4375-b24c-b750b0e4ea47.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/ca592e6f-a30c-4375-b24c-b750b0e4ea47.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-03-24 15:05:43 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b5317356426d8b3de9a6595f1e76, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5317356426d8b3de9a6595f1e76\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 15:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/ca592e6f-a30c-4375-b24c-b750b0e4ea47.jpg"}],"timestamp":1774335944278}}
