{"type":"message","id":"0987d46a","parentId":"6394305e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:16:47.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! All 15 documents have now been updated. Let me compile the final status report.\n\n**Completed (15/15 documents optimized):**\n\n行政子系统:\n- ✅ 1.1-DJOS-XZ: Iy8zwYL2fi5N5bkIRvucEOTXnoc\n- ✅ 1.2-DJMS-XZ: PpkCwYT4CiMnUbksalxc82Htnjc\n- ✅ 1.3-DJAS-XZ: L0Yfw2SfTiGjobkK5uBcs7I1n3g\n\n培训子系统:\n- ✅ 2.1-DJOS-PX: JJXnwUxqAiWhMwkDDrUcgL4Xnhe\n- ✅ 2.2-DJMS-PX: YLqfw9zkfiP6I7kgYz9cWOmVnVe\n- ✅ 2.3-DJAS-PX: UQpKwQJTRiOX5rksqtdceAllndq\n\n服务子系统:\n- ✅ 3.1-DJOS-FW: Gan5wUgLriUGbZklM5lcax6znF5\n- ✅ 3.2-DJMS-FW: NJvdwkF2RiGpbQk7xB2cmLm9nLb\n- ✅ 3.3-DJAS-FW: IXhwwpeS7iWblpkVHchcqrT4nJg\n\n营销子系统:\n- ✅ 4.1-DJOS-YX: GBrTdiJXIoPhqFxAFa2cXP2lnAb\n\n\n- ✅ 4.2-DJMS-YX: HN74wINaciZbr0kx0y5cgqfQnPj\n- ✅ 4.3-DJAS-YX: NdI4wO9eLitygXkMz55cuUgin3g\n\n产品子系统:\n- ✅ 5.1-DJOS-CP: U56PdpsBrojAmtxCNNkcM6BWnme\n- ✅ 5.2-DJMS-CP: DpVddUKR1o8XY5xuI4AcaHwcnFb\n- ✅ 5.3-DJAS-CP: DxIlwtcZmirNaWkOljycE4UEnQd\n\nAll 15 subsystem documents are now complete and formatted consistently across the three DJMS levels.","thinkingSignature":"c0c8355cede5b079e63b78cbe2ed26811c01af4e22a89957c87adf181953ebb6"},{"type":"text","text":"**全面修正完成！**\n\n**15个文档全部更新完毕：**\n\n| 子系统 | DJOS（执行层） | DJMS（管控层） | DJAS（应用层） |\n|--------|---------------|---------------|---------------|\n| **行政** | ✅ 1.1-DJOS-XZ | ✅ 1.2-DJMS-XZ | ✅ 1.3-DJAS-XZ |\n| **培训** | ✅ 2.1-DJOS-PX | ✅ 2.2-DJMS-PX | ✅ 2.3-DJAS-PX |\n| **服务** | ✅ 3.1-DJOS-FW | ✅ 3.2-DJMS-FW | ✅ 3.3-DJAS-FW |\n| **营销** | ✅ 4.1-DJOS-YX | ✅ 4.2-DJMS-YX | ✅ 4.3-DJAS-YX |\n| **产品** | ✅ 5.1-DJOS-CP | ✅ 5.2-DJMS-CP | ✅ 5.3-DJAS-CP |\n\n**本次修正内容：**\n- ✅ 4.2-DJMS-YX（营销管控系统）- 按标准7章格式重写\n- ✅ 4.3-DJAS-YX（营销应用系统）- 按标准7章格式重写\n- ✅ 5.1-DJOS-CP（产品操作系统）- 按标准7章格式重写\n- ✅ 5.2-DJMS-CP（产品管控系统）- 按标准7章格式创建\n- ✅ 5.3-DJAS-CP（产品应用系统）- 按标准7章格式重写\n\n**标准7章结构：**\n1. 前言（文档目的、适用范围、核心原则表格）\n2. 概述（定位与职责、模块架构表格）\n3. 一级流程（全景图、模块关联图）\n4. 各模块详细流程（模块职责、一级流程